Privacy Policy for TaskBunny
Effective Date: April 25, 2025

Introduction -

TaskBunny is a productivity app that helps you organize tasks, notes, finances, and more. We're committed to protecting your privacy.

Data Collection and Storage -

Local Storage Only: All your data is stored locally on your device.
No Data Transmission: We do not collect, transmit, or store any of your data on external servers.
No Personal Information: We don't require or collect personal information.

Third-Party Services-

TaskBunny does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

Data Security-
Your data security depends on your device's security. We recommend using device passcode protection and keeping your operating system updated.

Changes to Privacy Policy-
We may update this privacy policy as needed. Check the app or our website for the most current version.

Contact-
For questions about this privacy policy, contact us at: mahmoudshal84@gmail.com
